            "title": "Seasonal and geographical distribution of cave-dwelling bats in Romania: implications for conservation: Seasonal and geographical distribution of cave-dwelling bats",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Z. L.",
