            "title": "Mist netting bias, species accumulation curves, and the rediscovery of two bats on Montserrat (Lesser Antilles)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Roxanne J.",
                    "lastName": "Larsen"
                },
                {
